data.enText: a woman who stays at home to cook, clean, take care of the children, etc. while her husband or partner goes out to work

tr: a wife who manages a household while her husband earns the family income

value.def: A housewife is a married woman who does not have a paid job, but instead looks after her home and children.

example.tran: 来自布里斯班的42岁家庭主妇
